1
00:01:31,410 --> 00:01:34,048
=The Glamorous Night=

2
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:37,097
(Five years ago)

3
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:38,499
I said no, and that means no.

4
00:01:38,499 --> 00:01:39,299
That's my sister.

5
00:01:39,299 --> 00:01:40,340
What gives you the right?

6
00:01:40,779 --> 00:01:42,100
Because you don't make any money!

7
00:01:42,700 --> 00:01:44,740
We've supported her
all the way through high school.

8
00:01:44,820 --> 00:01:46,260
Now retaking a year?

9
00:01:46,779 --> 00:01:48,460
Our family can't afford it anymore.

10
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:49,219
Don't you get it?

11
00:01:50,100 --> 00:01:52,419
And she won't go to an average college?

12
00:01:52,859 --> 00:01:55,100
Did you even go to high school?

13
00:01:55,340 --> 00:01:56,139
No, because I knew

14
00:01:56,139 --> 00:01:58,740
I wasn't cut out for studying.
But Zixuan is different.

15
00:01:59,060 --> 00:01:59,939
How is she different?

16
00:02:00,019 --> 00:02:01,299
She's not cut out for studying!

17
00:02:01,620 --> 00:02:03,019
- And she's so ungrateful!
- You...

18
00:02:03,939 --> 00:02:05,900
Shut up! Just shut up! Go to your room!

19
00:02:06,579 --> 00:02:07,100
Zixuan!

20
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:08,219
Don't be upset.

21
00:02:10,180 --> 00:02:11,740
Mom, I'm going to my parents' place.

22
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:12,340
Wait.

23
00:02:13,060 --> 00:02:13,620
What?

24
00:02:15,939 --> 00:02:16,860
I won't retake a year.

25
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:36,872
(Imbalance: Wanting Both)

26
00:02:38,536 --> 00:02:42,475
=Episode 13=
(Sisters)

27
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:18,580
Are you not home?

28
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:19,259
What is it?

29
00:03:19,939 --> 00:03:20,499
Just tell me.

30
00:03:20,939 --> 00:03:21,939
You messed with the lock?

31
00:03:23,539 --> 00:03:24,860
You need to get this straight.

32
00:03:25,460 --> 00:03:26,740
I messed with the lock?

33
00:03:27,379 --> 00:03:28,659
I rented this apartment.

34
00:03:29,099 --> 00:03:30,779
My name is on the lease.

35
00:03:31,539 --> 00:03:33,379
You should be the one leaving.

36
00:03:35,699 --> 00:03:38,539
If it's okay with you,
can I crash at your place tonight?

37
00:03:38,939 --> 00:03:40,259
Then tomorrow, I'll...

38
00:03:40,499 --> 00:03:41,420
Of course, it's okay.

39
00:03:41,860 --> 00:03:43,180
But we're both at work right now.

40
00:03:43,219 --> 00:03:44,539
Just head over there and rest up.

41
00:03:45,379 --> 00:03:47,180
The key's under the doormat.

42
00:03:47,499 --> 00:03:49,060
We'll grab late-night snacks later.

43
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:50,219
Okay.

44
00:03:50,499 --> 00:03:51,539
My treat tonight.

45
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:33,139
(Two years ago)
Move aside. Move.

46
00:04:33,420 --> 00:04:34,780
Don't block the way.

47
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:36,060
How can anyone get through?

48
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:37,576
You don't even know the basic rules.

49
00:04:37,780 --> 00:04:39,379
How many fresh graduates know the rules?

50
00:04:41,499 --> 00:04:42,660
They're so cocky.

51
00:04:43,259 --> 00:04:44,139
Not worth it.

52
00:04:44,139 --> 00:04:45,379
The pay here is terrible.

53
00:04:45,379 --> 00:04:46,259
Just 4,000 a month.

54
00:04:46,259 --> 00:04:47,259
So why are you here?

55
00:04:47,699 --> 00:04:49,060
I'm from an ordinary college.

56
00:04:49,300 --> 00:04:50,100
But my dad said

57
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:52,379
I can find a job. He'll support me.
What about you?

58
00:04:52,379 --> 00:04:53,860
You can be a postpartum caregiver.

59
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:54,819
They make good money.

60
00:04:55,220 --> 00:04:55,819
Wang Yilin?

61
00:04:56,060 --> 00:04:56,740
Yes, here!

62
00:04:58,259 --> 00:04:58,980
I wish.

63
00:04:58,980 --> 00:05:00,259
But I know nothing about babies.

64
00:05:00,259 --> 00:05:01,259
I can't cook either.

65
00:05:01,259 --> 00:05:02,139
Most of all, I'm lazy.

66
00:05:04,296 --> 00:05:05,638
(UJCY Home Care)

67
00:05:07,834 --> 00:05:10,312
(Recruiting housekeepers)

68
00:05:31,740 --> 00:05:32,499
Hello, ma'am.

69
00:05:34,180 --> 00:05:35,180
My name is Zeng Zixuan.

70
00:05:35,220 --> 00:05:36,220
Here for a trial shift.

71
00:05:36,339 --> 00:05:36,899
Come on in.

72
00:05:37,499 --> 00:05:38,259
Put on slippers.

73
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:44,259
How was it?

74
00:05:45,060 --> 00:05:46,300
Do you like the braised pork?

75
00:05:46,660 --> 00:05:47,339
I love it.

76
00:05:47,499 --> 00:05:48,339
Thank you, sweetie.

77
00:06:03,579 --> 00:06:04,259
Excuse me?

78
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:06,579
I'm getting an ice cream.

79
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:29,019
(Didn't I tell you)

80
00:06:29,019 --> 00:06:30,139
(to be extra careful?)

81
00:06:30,139 --> 00:06:31,019
(Mind your words)

82
00:06:31,019 --> 00:06:32,060
(and your actions.)

83
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:33,300
(I didn't do anything!)

84
00:06:33,300 --> 00:06:34,060
(You didn't?)

85
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:35,579
(They rejected you with a mood)

86
00:06:35,699 --> 00:06:36,780
(and even scolded me!)

87
00:06:37,939 --> 00:06:40,100
(Forget it.
I don't want to talk to you anymore.)

88
00:06:40,819 --> 00:06:41,379
(Listen.)

89
00:06:41,579 --> 00:06:43,780
(You failed the trial. I can't pay you.)

90
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:45,380
(Requirements: Female,
with height of 168 cm)

91
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:47,416
(Education: Junior College or above.
Pleasant appearance, good temperament.)

92
00:06:49,352 --> 00:06:52,264
(Recruitment Position, Wine Promoter)

93
00:07:22,860 --> 00:07:23,899
Your interviewer

94
00:07:23,899 --> 00:07:24,939
could be a man

95
00:07:24,939 --> 00:07:26,060
or a woman.

96
00:07:26,139 --> 00:07:26,620
It's fine.

97
00:07:26,819 --> 00:07:29,819
Because they represent our company.

98
00:07:29,939 --> 00:07:31,780
Your company paid our company

99
00:07:32,459 --> 00:07:34,899
to be here and do our job.

100
00:07:35,420 --> 00:07:37,459
So we don't represent the boss.

101
00:07:37,939 --> 00:07:39,579
No matter what questions they ask,

102
00:07:40,060 --> 00:07:41,060
your answers

103
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:42,620
only need to emphasize one thing.

104
00:07:42,980 --> 00:07:43,740
Discretion.

105
00:07:44,100 --> 00:07:44,939
Then you win.

106
00:07:47,540 --> 00:07:48,939
I can't be too passionate about life

107
00:07:48,939 --> 00:07:51,339
and make the company
think I lack ambition.

108
00:07:51,339 --> 00:07:53,220
I can't be too career-driven,

109
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:54,100
which seems heartless.

110
00:07:54,339 --> 00:07:56,499
I can't focus solely on my own mission,

111
00:07:56,499 --> 00:07:58,740
and make the company think
I have a narrow vision.

112
00:07:58,740 --> 00:08:00,100
I can't be too lofty and detached,

113
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:03,139
otherwise, the company
might fear I'm after their job.

114
00:08:03,980 --> 00:08:04,939
This is not discretion.

115
00:08:06,060 --> 00:08:06,699
It's twisted.

116
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:07,780
Listen up.

117
00:08:08,339 --> 00:08:09,420
You can challenge the game,

118
00:08:09,540 --> 00:08:11,220
but never question the rules themselves.

119
00:08:14,980 --> 00:08:17,499
You should have coached me
on this earlier.

120
00:08:17,899 --> 00:08:19,780
Before, you were on the front lines.

121
00:08:20,180 --> 00:08:23,060
This coaching would've made you
aim high but achieve little.

122
00:08:23,860 --> 00:08:26,899
But at the director level,
your work only accounts for 30 percent.

123
00:08:27,139 --> 00:08:29,180
The rest is
about navigating relationships.

124
00:08:29,379 --> 00:08:31,100
Now's the perfect time
for this coaching.

125
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:03,380
I'll head back now.

126
00:09:04,739 --> 00:09:05,579
Be careful out there.

127
00:09:19,060 --> 00:09:22,219
Mr. Yu from Wan Jialing gave me a card

128
00:09:23,300 --> 00:09:24,859
as extra appreciation for my help.

129
00:09:28,616 --> 00:09:30,990
(One day ago)

130
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:39,540
You're better at swimming.

131
00:09:40,619 --> 00:09:41,300
Well,

132
00:09:42,219 --> 00:09:43,619
health is the foundation.

133
00:09:45,819 --> 00:09:48,420
Oh, and I've got the rebate ready.

134
00:09:48,859 --> 00:09:50,020
I was just about to tell you.

135
00:09:50,020 --> 00:09:51,060
I've talked with the boss.

136
00:09:51,060 --> 00:09:52,459
Your share is 120,000.

137
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:53,500
That's not necessary.

138
00:09:53,939 --> 00:09:54,699
That won't do!

139
00:09:54,739 --> 00:09:55,540
You must take it.

140
00:09:57,339 --> 00:09:58,459
If you insist on giving it,

141
00:09:59,140 --> 00:10:00,099
then give it to Hailun.

142
00:10:01,579 --> 00:10:02,219
Qiao Hailun?

143
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:05,660
Yes, she contributed
significantly to this project.

144
00:10:06,339 --> 00:10:08,459
You should contact her
about this directly,

145
00:10:08,579 --> 00:10:09,339
as if I don't know.

146
00:10:10,660 --> 00:10:11,660
How much is in there?

147
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:12,859
Quite a bit.

148
00:10:13,739 --> 00:10:14,500
120,000.

149
00:10:16,579 --> 00:10:17,380
Should I return it?

150
00:10:18,459 --> 00:10:19,859
If they give it to you, keep it.

151
00:10:26,699 --> 00:10:27,459
Thank you, Mr. Li.

152
00:10:31,339 --> 00:10:33,339
A client had an urgent issue coming up.

153
00:10:33,619 --> 00:10:34,540
I'm now in Shanghai.

154
00:10:42,939 --> 00:10:44,140
Hello, Ruijin Consulting.

155
00:10:44,780 --> 00:10:45,540
Hello.

156
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:46,619
May I talk to Qiao Hailun?

157
00:10:47,339 --> 00:10:48,420
You can try her extension.

158
00:10:49,060 --> 00:10:50,140
I did. No one answered.

159
00:10:50,140 --> 00:10:51,380
We have a call for 2 PM.

160
00:10:51,859 --> 00:10:52,859
Okay, hold on please.

161
00:10:56,859 --> 00:10:58,459
Qiao Hailun is away on urgent business.

162
00:10:58,459 --> 00:10:59,459
Try her mobile phone.

163
00:11:01,020 --> 00:11:01,699
Okay, thanks.

164
00:11:22,060 --> 00:11:22,540
Come in.

165
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:26,300
Ms. Zhao.

166
00:11:30,939 --> 00:11:31,780
Uh...

167
00:11:32,699 --> 00:11:33,699
About today...

168
00:11:34,540 --> 00:11:35,459
Perfect timing.

169
00:11:36,699 --> 00:11:37,780
The target

170
00:11:38,099 --> 00:11:40,180
of selling 50,000 cases in Q1
was actually my idea.

171
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:42,339
The company's annual target is 120,000.

172
00:11:42,339 --> 00:11:43,300
Keep that in mind.

173
00:11:45,219 --> 00:11:45,859
I understand.

174
00:11:47,459 --> 00:11:48,180
I meant to say,

175
00:11:48,619 --> 00:11:49,459
are you okay?

176
00:11:51,819 --> 00:11:52,619
I'm fine.

177
00:11:55,380 --> 00:11:57,540
You seemed

178
00:11:57,579 --> 00:12:00,020
preoccupied during the barbecue earlier.

179
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:01,459
It's rare.

180
00:12:02,099 --> 00:12:03,859
Maybe I didn't sleep well last night.

181
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:07,339
I don't think
you've been resting enough.

182
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:09,619
Why not take a few days off?

183
00:12:09,619 --> 00:12:10,380
I'll be around.

184
00:12:10,739 --> 00:12:11,300
No.

185
00:12:11,819 --> 00:12:12,780
Now is a crucial period.

186
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:13,459
I can't rest.

187
00:12:14,339 --> 00:12:14,979
By the way,

188
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:16,060
this Friday,

189
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:17,540
let's have a sales planning meeting.

190
00:12:18,859 --> 00:12:22,619
Pull the sales data
from previous years and key regions,

191
00:12:23,380 --> 00:12:25,260
along with competitors' data.

192
00:12:25,819 --> 00:12:27,020
We need to know our enemies.

193
00:12:32,180 --> 00:12:33,780
I'll get to work then.

194
00:12:34,219 --> 00:12:34,579
Okay.

195
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:09,739
Sir, didn't we agree
I'd repay next month?

196
00:13:12,819 --> 00:13:14,339
Who agreed to that?

197
00:13:14,420 --> 00:13:16,579
The neighborhood committee
promised demolition here.

198
00:13:17,099 --> 00:13:18,859
I'd get two apartments after that.

199
00:13:19,339 --> 00:13:20,699
Five years passed.

200
00:13:20,699 --> 00:13:21,739
Did anything happen?

201
00:13:22,020 --> 00:13:23,500
What good are promises?

202
00:13:23,819 --> 00:13:26,660
But... but I really
don't have the money now.

203
00:13:26,660 --> 00:13:27,699
No money, huh?

204
00:13:28,099 --> 00:13:29,180
Then pay with your life.

205
00:13:29,180 --> 00:13:29,859
No, no!

206
00:13:29,859 --> 00:13:30,819
No, please.

207
00:13:30,819 --> 00:13:32,339
I'll get it from my wife.

208
00:13:32,699 --> 00:13:33,819
I'll go talk to my wife.

209
00:13:33,819 --> 00:13:35,300
Where's your wife's money?

210
00:13:36,540 --> 00:13:38,219
She just bought a bag last month.

211
00:13:38,819 --> 00:13:40,219
That bag is very expensive.

212
00:13:40,219 --> 00:13:41,459
Please. Sir.

213
00:13:41,459 --> 00:13:43,140
How can there be a man like you?

214
00:13:43,459 --> 00:13:45,579
Actually scheming
to take your own wife's bag?

215
00:13:45,660 --> 00:13:46,339
Hit him!

216
00:13:54,459 --> 00:13:55,819
Sir, please stop hitting me.

217
00:13:55,900 --> 00:13:57,900
Kill me and no one will pay you back.

218
00:13:58,739 --> 00:14:01,219
Please, sir.

219
00:14:01,219 --> 00:14:03,459
Stop hitting me! Please.

220
00:14:13,576 --> 00:14:15,912
(Divorce Agreement)

221
00:14:17,859 --> 00:14:19,060
What's this?

222
00:14:19,219 --> 00:14:21,260
Do you know
where your wife got that bag?

223
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:25,459
She bought it.

224
00:14:26,699 --> 00:14:29,219
If she could afford
such an expensive bag herself,

225
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:32,699
how could she have been so blind
to marry a man like you?

226
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:35,099
Of course, someone gave it to her.

227
00:14:38,219 --> 00:14:39,420
Who gave it to her?

228
00:14:39,660 --> 00:14:41,020
Forget about it.

229
00:14:41,300 --> 00:14:44,020
It's someone neither you nor I
can afford to mess with.

230
00:14:44,579 --> 00:14:46,339
Get divorced from your wife right away.

231
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:49,260
Do me a favor, and do yourself a favor.

232
00:14:56,660 --> 00:14:57,619
Mr. Wu.

233
00:14:59,339 --> 00:15:00,579
Ms. Liang.

234
00:15:02,060 --> 00:15:03,660
Sorry, I went to buy a big cake.

235
00:15:03,660 --> 00:15:04,420
I'm late.

236
00:15:04,660 --> 00:15:06,339
No need to be so polite.

237
00:15:06,339 --> 00:15:07,859
- Come on.
- It's only proper.

238
00:15:07,859 --> 00:15:09,020
Let me introduce you.

239
00:15:11,060 --> 00:15:14,819
Everyone, this is Ms. Liang,
the beautiful saleslady.

240
00:15:14,939 --> 00:15:15,780
Isn't she pretty?

241
00:15:17,060 --> 00:15:18,380
Hello, everyone.

242
00:15:26,219 --> 00:15:26,939
Liang.

243
00:15:28,020 --> 00:15:28,859
Where is the wine?

244
00:15:29,420 --> 00:15:30,219
What wine?

245
00:15:30,339 --> 00:15:34,099
Didn't I tell you to bring
six extra bottles of Moonlight City?

246
00:15:34,420 --> 00:15:35,459
Did you tell me?

247
00:15:35,859 --> 00:15:36,939
Yes, I did.

248
00:15:36,979 --> 00:15:38,060
When did you say that?

249
00:15:38,099 --> 00:15:39,939
I told you long ago.

250
00:15:40,339 --> 00:15:41,180
Check your WeChat.

251
00:15:41,180 --> 00:15:42,099
Let me see.

252
00:15:43,699 --> 00:15:44,459
Look here.

253
00:15:44,939 --> 00:15:50,099
"Bring six extra bottles of Moonlight
City vintage for the birthday dinner."

254
00:15:50,260 --> 00:15:50,979
"No problem."

255
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:52,420
Exactly.

256
00:15:52,420 --> 00:15:52,859
Right?

257
00:15:53,699 --> 00:15:55,060
But look, there's more.

258
00:15:55,540 --> 00:15:56,300
"Sir,"

259
00:15:56,339 --> 00:16:00,260
"please pay for the six bottles
of Moonlight City vintage."

260
00:16:00,660 --> 00:16:01,339
"Company policy"

261
00:16:01,339 --> 00:16:04,699
"is orders over ten thousand
can't be delivered before payment."

262
00:16:05,060 --> 00:16:06,300
"Please understand."

263
00:16:06,300 --> 00:16:08,819
Then you said
you had no money in WeChat.

264
00:16:08,819 --> 00:16:10,739
"Could you pay for me first?"

265
00:16:10,739 --> 00:16:12,020
"I'll pay you back tomorrow."

266
00:16:12,939 --> 00:16:13,979
Half a month has passed.

267
00:16:16,180 --> 00:16:17,819
And I didn't pay you?

268
00:16:18,099 --> 00:16:18,699
No.

269
00:16:18,699 --> 00:16:20,660
Look, the chat stops right there.

270
00:16:21,339 --> 00:16:22,819
I'll pay you now. Right now.

271
00:16:22,819 --> 00:16:23,619
Hurry up.

272
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:25,339
And the wine?

273
00:16:25,459 --> 00:16:26,459
I brought the wine.

274
00:16:26,579 --> 00:16:27,579
It's in the trunk.

275
00:16:27,579 --> 00:16:28,420
I'll go get it now.

276
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:29,859
You brought it?

277
00:16:31,060 --> 00:16:32,099
Don't forget the money.

278
00:16:32,099 --> 00:16:33,219
You are smart as always.

279
00:16:33,219 --> 00:16:33,979
Transfer it.

280
00:16:35,380 --> 00:16:36,339
Hurry up! Hurry up!

281
00:16:36,339 --> 00:16:36,859
Okay, okay.

282
00:16:51,300 --> 00:16:51,939
What is it?

283
00:16:56,060 --> 00:16:56,739
Ms. Liang.

284
00:16:57,660 --> 00:17:00,020
Your husband has agreed
to sign the divorce papers.

285
00:17:00,699 --> 00:17:01,660
When can you come in?

286
00:17:02,699 --> 00:17:03,979
Let's all sit down together

287
00:17:04,179 --> 00:17:07,060
and sign your debt repayment agreement.

288
00:17:07,300 --> 00:17:08,579
Okay. Got it.

289
00:17:08,980 --> 00:17:09,740
It's a deal.

290
00:17:25,032 --> 00:17:33,320
(One month later)

291
00:17:39,300 --> 00:17:40,552
I got the divorce certificate.

292
00:18:04,020 --> 00:18:04,859
What's going on?

293
00:18:05,500 --> 00:18:06,379
Your look

294
00:18:07,419 --> 00:18:08,500
makes me uneasy.

295
00:18:08,819 --> 00:18:10,819
Did you make Yao Xiaohui
agree to the divorce?

296
00:18:11,540 --> 00:18:12,139
Yes.

297
00:18:12,619 --> 00:18:13,339
Why?

298
00:18:14,060 --> 00:18:15,912
Didn't you insist
on one-on-one relationship?

299
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:18,300
I hate waiting more than anything.

300
00:18:24,659 --> 00:18:26,139
Do you know what that building is?

301
00:18:26,700 --> 00:18:27,460
Of course, I do.

302
00:18:28,060 --> 00:18:28,980
The White Swan Hotel.

303
00:18:30,099 --> 00:18:31,700
Every Guangzhou local knows it.

304
00:18:32,819 --> 00:18:34,700
China's first five-star hotel.

305
00:18:36,020 --> 00:18:37,579
My home is right across from it.

306
00:18:38,460 --> 00:18:39,419
When I was little,

307
00:18:39,419 --> 00:18:41,540
I used to walk and run here.

308
00:18:42,179 --> 00:18:44,020
I'd just stare at this White Swan Hotel,

309
00:18:44,379 --> 00:18:45,300
thinking to myself,

310
00:18:46,300 --> 00:18:47,700
"Once I grow up and make money,"

311
00:18:48,260 --> 00:18:50,260
"I must stay at the White Swan Hotel
for a night."

312
00:18:51,300 --> 00:18:53,940
"I'll enjoy Guangzhou's
beautiful scenery and delicious food."

313
00:18:57,379 --> 00:18:59,819
But that dream still hasn't come true.

314
00:19:00,260 --> 00:19:01,540
Even though I've stayed at many

315
00:19:01,540 --> 00:19:03,419
more luxurious five-star hotels
than this one.

316
00:19:05,220 --> 00:19:05,700
Why?

317
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:09,619
Because I haven't met someone
worth sharing it with.

318
00:19:17,099 --> 00:19:18,419
Understood. I'll arrange it.

319
00:19:18,859 --> 00:19:19,379
Tomorrow?

320
00:19:19,659 --> 00:19:20,220
Today.

321
00:19:22,460 --> 00:19:24,060
I also hate waiting.

322
00:19:28,659 --> 00:19:29,096
Let's go!

323
00:19:31,579 --> 00:19:32,139
Let's go!

324
00:19:45,179 --> 00:19:45,700
Tang.

325
00:19:45,780 --> 00:19:47,220
This... this is too generous.

326
00:19:49,020 --> 00:19:50,260
All premium goods!

327
00:19:51,619 --> 00:19:54,419
If they weren't premium ones, would I
dare offer them to you, Mr. Cai?

328
00:19:54,419 --> 00:19:55,300
Just call me Cai.

329
00:19:55,300 --> 00:19:56,379
No need for the formality.

330
00:19:57,460 --> 00:19:59,020
This is too valuable.

331
00:20:00,540 --> 00:20:01,339
Rest assured.

332
00:20:01,740 --> 00:20:02,859
I have plenty of quotas.

333
00:20:03,139 --> 00:20:04,619
Come to me again when you want more.

334
00:20:05,300 --> 00:20:06,379
Thank you so much.

335
00:20:06,899 --> 00:20:08,139
Why be polite with me?

336
00:20:10,579 --> 00:20:11,899
We're all on the same side now.

337
00:20:12,179 --> 00:20:14,300
I'll speak frankly about something.

338
00:20:15,139 --> 00:20:15,540
Go ahead.

339
00:20:17,379 --> 00:20:19,899
Qi Youlan instructed
the consulting firm to arrange

340
00:20:20,619 --> 00:20:23,260
executive interviews
for Dong Yue and Zhao Mei.

341
00:20:25,220 --> 00:20:25,980
Just them two?

342
00:20:26,740 --> 00:20:27,460
Just them two.

343
00:20:31,859 --> 00:20:34,700
Since that incident with Xu,

344
00:20:35,220 --> 00:20:37,419
the position of Director
isn't so glamorous anymore.

345
00:20:39,099 --> 00:20:41,579
Besides, with so many people watching,

346
00:20:42,419 --> 00:20:43,460
it's inconvenient.

347
00:20:44,139 --> 00:20:45,379
And business is tough.

348
00:20:46,379 --> 00:20:47,500
Targets keep increasing.

349
00:20:51,220 --> 00:20:51,940
Tang,

350
00:20:52,740 --> 00:20:53,859
don't take it to heart.

351
00:20:55,819 --> 00:20:57,060
I'm fine.

352
00:20:57,940 --> 00:20:58,980
Don't worry about me.

353
00:21:00,940 --> 00:21:02,344
I don't care who the Director is,

354
00:21:03,780 --> 00:21:05,379
as long as they don't get in my way.

355
00:21:06,339 --> 00:21:06,859
Excuse me.

356
00:21:06,859 --> 00:21:07,460
Hello.

357
00:21:07,460 --> 00:21:08,500
Give me some sanqi herbs.

358
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:09,060
Okay.

359
00:21:09,899 --> 00:21:11,419
Mine are better.

360
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:13,700
Bigger ones.

361
00:21:13,700 --> 00:21:14,540
Thanks.

362
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:15,460
The best.

363
00:21:15,899 --> 00:21:16,859
You're back.

364
00:21:16,859 --> 00:21:17,859
Enough weight.

365
00:21:18,139 --> 00:21:18,819
Just these two.

366
00:21:19,300 --> 00:21:19,940
Uncle.

367
00:21:20,099 --> 00:21:21,020
Mei, you're back!

368
00:21:21,500 --> 00:21:22,500
Haven't seen you in ages!

369
00:21:22,619 --> 00:21:23,819
I have been too busy lately.

370
00:21:24,179 --> 00:21:25,740
All three of your family are busy,

371
00:21:25,980 --> 00:21:27,500
making money hand over fist.

372
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:29,500
What's the fun in not making money?

373
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:31,619
Come support us more often.

374
00:21:31,859 --> 00:21:32,700
Support us more.

375
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:34,740
Mei, you're back.

376
00:21:35,060 --> 00:21:37,619
- Where are my parents?
- They went to restock.

377
00:21:38,300 --> 00:21:39,260
Perfect timing.

378
00:21:39,260 --> 00:21:41,540
- Watch the shop. I go to the restroom.
- Okay, go ahead.

379
00:21:41,540 --> 00:21:42,300
Thanks!

380
00:21:43,700 --> 00:21:45,700
Hey, how much for this fish maw?

381
00:21:46,579 --> 00:21:49,020
The small yellow bass maw
is 680 yuan per half a kilogram.

382
00:21:49,980 --> 00:21:50,659
Can I look?

383
00:21:50,659 --> 00:21:51,379
Here, take a look.

384
00:21:54,179 --> 00:21:55,659
These are a bit small.

385
00:21:55,940 --> 00:21:56,899
Got anything better?

386
00:21:57,139 --> 00:21:57,819
Nicer looking?

387
00:21:58,300 --> 00:21:59,619
For yourself or as a gift?

388
00:21:59,940 --> 00:22:00,700
A gift.

389
00:22:00,859 --> 00:22:01,700
For gifting?

390
00:22:02,700 --> 00:22:03,740
This is good for gifts.

391
00:22:04,500 --> 00:22:06,780
Bigger size, and thicker collagen.

392
00:22:06,899 --> 00:22:07,619
Take a look.

393
00:22:07,619 --> 00:22:08,940
True connoisseurs will know.

394
00:22:09,980 --> 00:22:11,139
How much is this?

395
00:22:11,139 --> 00:22:12,339
1,800 per half a kilogram.

396
00:22:12,940 --> 00:22:13,700
How many pieces?

397
00:22:13,700 --> 00:22:14,540
33.

398
00:22:15,139 --> 00:22:16,659
Good, but a bit pricey.

399
00:22:16,980 --> 00:22:18,940
You get what you pay for.

400
00:22:19,460 --> 00:22:20,980
Our shop's been open for fifty years.

401
00:22:20,980 --> 00:22:22,579
(Every time I'm unhappy,)

402
00:22:23,060 --> 00:22:25,540
(I unconsciously walk back
to this dried goods shop.)

403
00:22:26,579 --> 00:22:28,780
(As if some force is pulling me back.)

404
00:22:29,579 --> 00:22:31,700
(It reminds me where I started,)

405
00:22:32,060 --> 00:22:34,940
(simplifying all complicated feelings.)

406
00:22:36,099 --> 00:22:38,024
(The emotions I wanted to vent)

407
00:22:38,599 --> 00:22:41,379
(quietly dissolved just like that.)

408
00:22:45,220 --> 00:22:46,540
What's going on?

409
00:22:47,619 --> 00:22:48,940
Drinking this early at noon?

410
00:22:49,819 --> 00:22:50,859
My divorce is finalized.

411
00:22:53,099 --> 00:22:53,940
It's done?

412
00:22:55,139 --> 00:22:56,460
How did Yao Xiaohui agree?

413
00:22:56,700 --> 00:22:57,220
Guess.

414
00:23:00,540 --> 00:23:01,020
Shen Mo.

415
00:23:02,980 --> 00:23:04,260
The moment Shen Mo stepped in,

416
00:23:04,260 --> 00:23:05,500
Yao Xiaohui just backed down.

417
00:23:05,819 --> 00:23:06,579
Exactly.

418
00:23:06,579 --> 00:23:08,020
Hurry! Congratulate me!

419
00:23:10,300 --> 00:23:12,419
Seriously, today's a big day for me.

420
00:23:18,460 --> 00:23:19,139
Feels amazing.

421
00:23:19,300 --> 00:23:21,540
So you and Shen Mo will...

422
00:23:22,619 --> 00:23:23,500
Start dating.

423
00:23:24,339 --> 00:23:25,980
Dating without talking about the future.

424
00:23:27,780 --> 00:23:29,619
We're flying
to Changbai Mountains tonight.

425
00:23:30,379 --> 00:23:32,840
He said it's snowing up north
and he will take me on vacation.

426
00:23:34,740 --> 00:23:36,899
I haven't been on vacation in years.

427
00:23:36,899 --> 00:23:39,099
And I haven't seen snow in ages either.

428
00:23:41,379 --> 00:23:42,220
But don't worry,

429
00:23:43,099 --> 00:23:44,540
even if Shen Mo and I date,

430
00:23:44,700 --> 00:23:46,179
I'll never betray you.

431
00:23:57,099 --> 00:23:58,220
What's up? What's wrong?

432
00:24:13,859 --> 00:24:15,179
Li Dongming is cheating on me.

433
00:24:22,700 --> 00:24:23,300
This

434
00:24:23,300 --> 00:24:25,899
is a photo I took of them in Shanghai.

435
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:27,700
This girl

436
00:24:27,700 --> 00:24:30,300
is a junior analyst at their company.

437
00:24:30,700 --> 00:24:32,500
Last time,
I already felt something was off.

438
00:24:32,500 --> 00:24:34,300
Later, Li Dongming
said they had layoffs,

439
00:24:34,300 --> 00:24:35,300
and she was one of them.

440
00:24:35,300 --> 00:24:36,339
So I let it go.

441
00:24:37,020 --> 00:24:37,940
Only now do I realize

442
00:24:37,940 --> 00:24:39,099
that she has stayed.

443
00:24:39,619 --> 00:24:40,540
On his business trip,

444
00:24:40,899 --> 00:24:41,859
Li Dongming took her.

445
00:24:47,540 --> 00:24:48,540
Did you know?

446
00:24:49,940 --> 00:24:51,659
Yes, I knew.

447
00:24:54,579 --> 00:24:55,700
Then why didn't you tell me?

448
00:24:57,220 --> 00:24:59,060
I accidentally saw them once.

449
00:24:59,619 --> 00:25:01,060
And it was at night.

450
00:25:02,220 --> 00:25:02,940
I wasn't sure.

451
00:25:03,819 --> 00:25:04,619
On the street,

452
00:25:04,619 --> 00:25:06,460
I wasn't sure
if they were having an affair.

453
00:25:07,579 --> 00:25:08,940
Li Dongming has social dinners.

454
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:10,859
Who knows
if he was just putting on an act?

455
00:25:12,899 --> 00:25:14,419
I was afraid you'd think

456
00:25:14,419 --> 00:25:15,940
I was gossiping or annoying.

457
00:25:15,940 --> 00:25:17,379
You weren't afraid of that.

458
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:20,940
You just thought you had warned me

459
00:25:20,940 --> 00:25:22,500
about marrying him before, but I even

460
00:25:22,500 --> 00:25:23,579
defended him.

461
00:25:23,780 --> 00:25:25,020
So now you won't tell me

462
00:25:25,020 --> 00:25:25,780
that he's cheating?

463
00:25:27,540 --> 00:25:28,260
It's not the same!

464
00:25:28,260 --> 00:25:29,819
He's sleeping with her now!

465
00:25:34,179 --> 00:25:35,619
In your eyes, I'm just a fool.

466
00:25:41,740 --> 00:25:44,220
Yeah, you are a fool, Zhao Mei.

467
00:25:45,700 --> 00:25:46,940
You're such a smart person!

468
00:25:47,099 --> 00:25:48,859
Don't you know who Li Dongming is?

469
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:50,020
But you didn't care!

470
00:25:50,220 --> 00:25:52,460
So why would I bother tattling to you?

471
00:25:52,460 --> 00:25:53,780
Totally unnecessary, right?

472
00:25:54,700 --> 00:25:56,139
I'd just be meddling.

473
00:25:56,139 --> 00:25:57,540
Why would I do that?

474
00:25:59,060 --> 00:26:00,260
Ladies, your dishes are ready.

475
00:26:02,940 --> 00:26:05,980
Yeah, I am a fool.

476
00:26:10,379 --> 00:26:11,139
Here you go.

477
00:26:11,139 --> 00:26:11,859
Check please.

478
00:26:12,220 --> 00:26:12,619
Okay.

479
00:26:26,419 --> 00:26:26,780
Let's go.

480
00:26:28,300 --> 00:26:28,700
Nice shot!

481
00:26:28,700 --> 00:26:29,419
Great shot!

482
00:26:32,220 --> 00:26:32,819
Over here!

483
00:26:33,300 --> 00:26:33,740
Got it!

484
00:26:34,339 --> 00:26:34,780
Nice!

485
00:26:35,020 --> 00:26:35,500
Hey.

486
00:26:37,460 --> 00:26:38,179
Okay, thanks.

487
00:26:40,940 --> 00:26:41,980
It's been a while.

488
00:26:42,179 --> 00:26:42,460
Great!

489
00:26:42,540 --> 00:26:44,099
I got tired after playing.

490
00:26:44,099 --> 00:26:45,740
Your skills surprised me.

491
00:26:46,460 --> 00:26:48,700
I was on the school team
in middle school.

492
00:26:49,740 --> 00:26:50,472
You know,

493
00:26:51,899 --> 00:26:53,740
I called you over today

494
00:26:55,780 --> 00:26:57,260
to share something heartfelt.

495
00:26:57,500 --> 00:26:58,379
Come on.

496
00:26:58,379 --> 00:26:59,139
Speak your mind.

497
00:27:00,379 --> 00:27:00,980
Look.

498
00:27:01,859 --> 00:27:03,300
You've joined us for years now.

499
00:27:04,419 --> 00:27:06,099
You should know me pretty well.

500
00:27:07,099 --> 00:27:08,099
The thing about me is

501
00:27:09,339 --> 00:27:10,300
I lack ambition.

502
00:27:11,460 --> 00:27:12,540
Besides, I'm getting old.

503
00:27:13,300 --> 00:27:15,700
I just want to eat, drink, and have fun.

504
00:27:16,700 --> 00:27:18,460
The title like Director,

505
00:27:19,540 --> 00:27:20,579
I saw through it long ago.

506
00:27:21,619 --> 00:27:22,379
But

507
00:27:23,619 --> 00:27:25,220
I hope the new director

508
00:27:27,432 --> 00:27:28,179
is you,

509
00:27:29,099 --> 00:27:30,060
not Zhao Mei.

510
00:27:32,940 --> 00:27:33,740
Why?

511
00:27:34,460 --> 00:27:35,500
I can't accept it.

512
00:27:37,220 --> 00:27:38,419
You joined the company late.

513
00:27:39,740 --> 00:27:41,179
When you met Zhao Mei,

514
00:27:41,179 --> 00:27:45,220
she was probably a Promotions Manager.

515
00:27:45,220 --> 00:27:46,260
But I'm different.

516
00:27:47,099 --> 00:27:49,260
When I met Zhao Mei,
she was just a rookie,

517
00:27:50,659 --> 00:27:52,460
the most junior promoter.

518
00:27:53,099 --> 00:27:54,020
To put it bluntly,

519
00:27:54,020 --> 00:27:56,460
all she did was to fetch my glasses
and wipe my tables.

520
00:27:56,899 --> 00:27:57,780
Think about it.

521
00:27:58,540 --> 00:28:00,899
Suddenly, she's climbing over my head

522
00:28:01,020 --> 00:28:02,780
to be my boss.

523
00:28:05,940 --> 00:28:06,659
Got it.

524
00:28:07,700 --> 00:28:09,940
When someone who was just a stablehand

525
00:28:10,300 --> 00:28:12,099
is now leading the herd,

526
00:28:13,260 --> 00:28:16,020
who can accept it? No one can accept it.

527
00:28:17,700 --> 00:28:18,379
So,

528
00:28:20,220 --> 00:28:21,179
I'm on your side.

529
00:28:23,339 --> 00:28:24,020
I see.

530
00:28:24,020 --> 00:28:27,980
But in the end,
it depends on what the bosses think.

531
00:28:29,220 --> 00:28:30,220
I get it.

532
00:28:30,300 --> 00:28:32,940
The big boss
is buttering up headquarters,

533
00:28:33,460 --> 00:28:35,940
saying the executives lack a woman.

534
00:28:35,940 --> 00:28:37,060
They need to fill that gap.

535
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:39,260
But let's be real,

536
00:28:39,940 --> 00:28:43,260
does headquarters really care
that much about gender?

537
00:28:43,260 --> 00:28:44,220
Nonsense.

538
00:28:44,659 --> 00:28:46,099
They're running a business.

539
00:28:46,099 --> 00:28:47,260
They want to make money.

540
00:28:47,659 --> 00:28:50,940
If the China division tanks,

541
00:28:51,220 --> 00:28:53,419
forget about promoting
a female executive,

542
00:28:53,740 --> 00:28:57,460
even if Barry turned into a woman,

543
00:28:58,179 --> 00:28:59,419
it still wouldn't work.

544
00:29:00,260 --> 00:29:02,619
What if Zhao Mei actually
makes something of herself?

545
00:29:03,220 --> 00:29:04,859
You never know, right?

546
00:29:05,139 --> 00:29:07,220
I've actually thought about that.

547
00:29:08,780 --> 00:29:13,020
Isn't the company
doing executive interviews now?

548
00:29:13,700 --> 00:29:14,500
I was thinking that

549
00:29:15,220 --> 00:29:17,899
you can get those big clients
in Guangzhou to source from you.

550
00:29:18,099 --> 00:29:21,700
Then Zhao Mei's sales
would all go under your name, right?

551
00:29:21,700 --> 00:29:23,260
I wouldn't dare suggest that.

552
00:29:23,260 --> 00:29:24,619
Those major clients won't agree.

553
00:29:24,619 --> 00:29:25,460
Don't worry about it.

554
00:29:25,940 --> 00:29:26,700
I'll bring it up.

555
00:29:27,940 --> 00:29:31,379
But the sales subsidy
has to come from your end. Deal?

556
00:29:38,579 --> 00:29:39,780
Hold on.

557
00:29:45,980 --> 00:29:46,940
I need to see you.

558
00:29:47,260 --> 00:29:48,659
Now. Immediately. Right away.

559
00:29:49,260 --> 00:29:50,099
If you keep avoiding,

560
00:29:50,099 --> 00:29:51,220
I'll come to your office.

561
00:29:51,940 --> 00:29:52,780
Where are you?

562
00:29:53,300 --> 00:29:53,899
Your place.

563
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:56,220
Okay, I'm coming.

564
00:29:58,460 --> 00:29:59,460
Sir, I'm sorry.

565
00:29:59,460 --> 00:30:00,700
I will skip lunch.

566
00:30:00,700 --> 00:30:02,300
Something urgent came up. I gotta go.

567
00:30:02,300 --> 00:30:03,540
Go handle your business.

568
00:30:04,220 --> 00:30:05,859
But about what I just mentioned...

569
00:30:07,260 --> 00:30:08,260
No problem. Let's do it.

570
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:09,339
It's settled.

571
00:30:10,260 --> 00:30:11,060
Sure.

572
00:30:13,700 --> 00:30:16,220
Remember to call me
for stuff like this more often.

573
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:17,179
I need to get moving.

574
00:30:17,179 --> 00:30:17,659
Sure thing.

575
00:30:18,460 --> 00:30:19,139
See you.

576
00:30:25,859 --> 00:30:27,379
Great! Nice shot!

577
00:30:35,300 --> 00:30:36,020
Zhao Mei.

578
00:30:46,940 --> 00:30:47,859
I'm sorry.

579
00:30:48,179 --> 00:30:49,500
I won't mess around anymore.

580
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:50,740
I've been good these days.

581
00:30:50,859 --> 00:30:51,859
I haven't gone anywhere.

582
00:30:52,419 --> 00:30:53,579
They asked me to hang out.

583
00:30:53,579 --> 00:30:54,940
I just wanted to unwind a bit.

584
00:30:54,940 --> 00:30:56,139
Nothing happened.

585
00:30:56,179 --> 00:30:57,899
I love you. It's always been you.

586
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,500
Let's not break up, okay?

587
00:31:02,540 --> 00:31:03,379
Let go first.

588
00:31:03,859 --> 00:31:05,179
Let go. We can't talk like this.

589
00:31:09,020 --> 00:31:10,859
I know you love me too.

590
00:31:11,619 --> 00:31:12,700
While you were gone,

591
00:31:13,060 --> 00:31:13,940
I've been here.

592
00:31:13,940 --> 00:31:15,060
I lay in your bed,

593
00:31:15,060 --> 00:31:16,099
covered by your blanket.

594
00:31:17,020 --> 00:31:18,179
I imagined I was you.

595
00:31:18,859 --> 00:31:20,339
Suddenly, I understood you.

596
00:31:22,099 --> 00:31:22,659
About what?

597
00:31:23,260 --> 00:31:25,460
I know I have many flaws.

598
00:31:25,460 --> 00:31:26,819
I'll work hard to fix them.

599
00:31:27,220 --> 00:31:28,500
I've thought it through.

600
00:31:28,740 --> 00:31:31,339
The biggest obstacle
between us is my dad.

601
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:34,659
Yeah, I go to the restroom.

602
00:31:38,980 --> 00:31:39,899
I'm telling you,

603
00:31:40,179 --> 00:31:41,700
as long as you quit GST,

604
00:31:42,139 --> 00:31:44,260
he won't be able
to boss you around anymore.

605
00:31:46,339 --> 00:31:48,980
I'm telling you,
this really isn't a good job.

606
00:31:51,099 --> 00:31:53,780
I have many friends
who started their own companies.

607
00:31:53,780 --> 00:31:55,899
I'll let you meet them.
We can start our own business.

608
00:31:55,899 --> 00:31:57,020
I won't quit.

609
00:31:57,899 --> 00:31:58,740
Why?

610
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:01,619
You wouldn't understand.

611
00:32:01,659 --> 00:32:02,780
Try me.

612
00:32:02,780 --> 00:32:04,819
How can I know if you don't tell me?

613
00:32:08,700 --> 00:32:10,184
I know you don't like my job.

614
00:32:10,280 --> 00:32:11,700
You think it's chaotic, noisy,

615
00:32:11,819 --> 00:32:12,659
complicated,

616
00:32:12,780 --> 00:32:13,700
and involves drinking.

617
00:32:13,980 --> 00:32:14,940
But no one's forcing me.

618
00:32:14,940 --> 00:32:16,099
I chose this job myself.

619
00:32:16,099 --> 00:32:17,419
Do you actually like it?

620
00:32:17,700 --> 00:32:18,700
Yes, I do.

621
00:32:18,899 --> 00:32:21,139
In this line of work,
if you don't genuinely like it,

622
00:32:21,339 --> 00:32:22,859
you won't last a week.

623
00:32:23,179 --> 00:32:24,139
The constant drinking

624
00:32:24,419 --> 00:32:25,260
will repel you.

625
00:32:26,300 --> 00:32:27,300
Why?

626
00:32:27,619 --> 00:32:29,500
I always thought music
was your true passion.

627
00:32:30,379 --> 00:32:32,339
Yes, and also liquor.

628
00:32:36,020 --> 00:32:37,659
My father genuinely likes liquor too,

629
00:32:38,020 --> 00:32:38,980
but he has one more.

630
00:32:39,139 --> 00:32:39,940
He also likes women.

631
00:32:40,619 --> 00:32:42,099
So, will you become like him?

632
00:32:42,099 --> 00:32:43,139
Will you hook up daily?

633
00:32:43,139 --> 00:32:44,379
You've been out for days.

634
00:32:44,899 --> 00:32:46,659
Do you already have
someone else out there?

635
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:48,500
You...

636
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:50,020
I knew it!

637
00:32:50,419 --> 00:32:52,700
I told you long ago
this job would corrupt you.

638
00:32:52,780 --> 00:32:54,579
It'll turn you into someone like him.

639
00:32:54,780 --> 00:32:56,020
Tell me, who is it?

640
00:32:56,460 --> 00:32:58,179
A hostess or some wealthy woman?

641
00:32:58,540 --> 00:32:59,819
Look, I have plans later.

642
00:32:59,819 --> 00:33:00,740
Let's talk another day.

643
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:04,300
We're not done.

644
00:33:05,859 --> 00:33:08,260
You're not rational now.
We'll talk when you calm down.

645
00:33:08,419 --> 00:33:09,500
I am perfectly calm now.

646
00:33:09,579 --> 00:33:10,179
If you leave,

647
00:33:10,179 --> 00:33:11,460
it will mean we didn't break up.

648
00:33:11,940 --> 00:33:13,220
Just give me some time to think.

649
00:33:13,220 --> 00:33:13,980
Think about it now.

650
00:33:16,220 --> 00:33:16,740
We should...

651
00:33:16,740 --> 00:33:17,300
Stop!

652
00:33:21,460 --> 00:33:22,179
We'll talk again.

653
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:22,980
Just go.

654
00:33:25,700 --> 00:33:27,020
If you really like your job,

655
00:33:27,020 --> 00:33:28,179
we shouldn't break up.

656
00:33:28,540 --> 00:33:29,700
As long as you're in GST,

657
00:33:29,700 --> 00:33:30,859
my father won't give up.

658
00:33:30,859 --> 00:33:31,819
I'm doing this for you.

659
00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:36,579
(Now when I travel for work,)

660
00:34:37,259 --> 00:34:38,139
(I always take her.)

661
00:34:41,420 --> 00:34:43,659
(She's helped me rediscover something.)

662
00:34:45,579 --> 00:34:46,340
(What is it?)

663
00:34:50,380 --> 00:34:55,299
(It's that sense of control
I used to have over Zhao Mei.)

664
00:35:09,099 --> 00:35:09,460
Cheers.

665
00:35:09,460 --> 00:35:10,380
Hello.

666
00:35:12,699 --> 00:35:13,900
(Liang Danning was right.)

667
00:35:14,619 --> 00:35:17,139
(The moment I laid eyes on Li Dongming,)

668
00:35:17,659 --> 00:35:21,060
(I knew he was essentially
the same kind of person as Xu Yuntian.)

669
00:35:22,139 --> 00:35:25,779
(But I thought Li Dongming would be
a bit smarter than Xu Yuntian,)

670
00:35:25,940 --> 00:35:27,060
(and with more grace.)

671
00:35:27,500 --> 00:35:30,139
(I believed my strong heart
could handle it.)

672
00:35:32,420 --> 00:35:33,540
(Turns out I was wrong.)

673
00:35:34,179 --> 00:35:35,820
(Li Dongming isn't smart,)

674
00:35:36,060 --> 00:35:37,219
(nor graceful,)

675
00:35:37,820 --> 00:35:40,500
(and my heart isn't strong at all.)

676
00:35:41,299 --> 00:35:43,219
(Maybe this is fate's arrangement.)

677
00:35:43,860 --> 00:35:45,820
(I brought all this on myself.)

678
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:47,579
(I can't blame anyone else.)

679
00:35:48,739 --> 00:35:49,900
(I feel so tired.)

680
00:35:50,500 --> 00:35:51,739
(After every previous fight,)

681
00:35:51,900 --> 00:35:53,060
(I'd tell myself,)

682
00:35:53,900 --> 00:35:54,500
(Dong Yue,)

683
00:35:55,460 --> 00:35:57,980
(whoever wants something
has to pay the price.)

684
00:35:58,900 --> 00:36:00,460
(You can't have it all.)

685
00:36:01,380 --> 00:36:02,259
(Move-in Ready Apartments for Urgent Sale)
(Compared to Xu Yuntian,)

686
00:36:02,259 --> 00:36:04,460
(at least I don't have to jump
to catch my boss's bag.)

687
00:36:05,020 --> 00:36:06,380
(Besides, Shen Xing isn't old.)

688
00:36:06,380 --> 00:36:07,540
(She's somewhat beautiful.)

689
00:36:08,579 --> 00:36:11,420
(For a long time,
I thought I could adapt to this life.)

690
00:36:11,592 --> 00:36:12,579
♪Work can't stop♪

691
00:36:12,579 --> 00:36:13,900
(As long as I got what I wanted,)

692
00:36:14,259 --> 00:36:15,060
(I could adapt.)

693
00:36:16,060 --> 00:36:17,460
(But I truly can't.)

694
00:36:18,820 --> 00:36:20,139
(If this goes on, I don't know)

695
00:36:20,820 --> 00:36:22,219
(what kind of person I'll become.)

696
00:36:24,104 --> 00:36:26,423
♪Silent and unnoticed♪

697
00:36:26,423 --> 00:36:27,752
♪You've poured out♪

698
00:36:27,752 --> 00:36:29,909
♪All your sorrow♪

699
00:36:29,909 --> 00:36:32,340
♪But no one cares at all♪

700
00:36:32,340 --> 00:36:34,020
When they talked me into buying it,

701
00:36:34,139 --> 00:36:36,900
the area behind was still wilderness.

702
00:36:37,460 --> 00:36:40,020
I thought, since it wasn't expensive,

703
00:36:40,540 --> 00:36:41,820
I'd do my friend a favor

704
00:36:42,139 --> 00:36:42,739
and buy two.

705
00:36:43,259 --> 00:36:46,460
I never expected
they'd develop it so well later. Look.

706
00:36:47,060 --> 00:36:48,699
You've got great taste.

707
00:36:48,699 --> 00:36:50,020
This house is really beautiful.

708
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:51,940
You can even ski here.

709
00:36:52,299 --> 00:36:53,179
- Look.
- Skiing?

710
00:36:53,980 --> 00:36:54,820
Do you ski?

711
00:36:55,820 --> 00:36:56,579
A little,

712
00:36:56,779 --> 00:36:57,820
on intermediate slope.

713
00:36:58,179 --> 00:37:00,779
Really?
People from the south rarely ski.

714
00:37:01,340 --> 00:37:02,020
Impressive.

715
00:37:02,980 --> 00:37:04,219
Whatever my clients are into,

716
00:37:04,540 --> 00:37:05,420
I learn a little.

717
00:37:05,779 --> 00:37:07,060
I paid for the lessons myself.

718
00:37:08,299 --> 00:37:09,420
You're amazing.

719
00:37:10,020 --> 00:37:11,060
I'm alright.

720
00:37:11,219 --> 00:37:14,299
From here, you can ski down this way.

721
00:37:15,619 --> 00:37:16,579
Let me take this call.

722
00:37:16,579 --> 00:37:16,980
Okay.

723
00:37:19,380 --> 00:37:20,219
Danning.

724
00:37:21,219 --> 00:37:24,579
I'm really heartbroken right now.

725
00:37:25,739 --> 00:37:27,420
I feel awful.

726
00:37:28,259 --> 00:37:29,219
I know, I know.

727
00:37:29,380 --> 00:37:30,219
Where are you now?

728
00:37:30,980 --> 00:37:31,860
I'm at home.

729
00:37:32,328 --> 00:37:34,795
♪With countless lights on,
is someone heartbroken again♪

730
00:37:36,380 --> 00:37:37,020
Wait for me.

731
00:37:37,020 --> 00:37:38,060
I'm coming to see you now.

732
00:37:40,619 --> 00:37:41,380
Really?

733
00:37:43,219 --> 00:37:44,940
What about Changbai Mountains?

734
00:37:45,380 --> 00:37:46,139
It's okay.

735
00:37:46,579 --> 00:37:47,860
Wait for me. Bye.

736
00:37:48,168 --> 00:37:49,000
♪Locking dreams away in a drawer♪

737
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:50,152
♪Just to earn some meager profit♪

738
00:37:50,152 --> 00:37:51,500
♪No matter how hard I try,
it only brings sobs♪

739
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:53,460
Sorry, I have an emergency.

740
00:37:53,779 --> 00:37:55,099
Can you go ahead first?

741
00:37:55,099 --> 00:37:56,579
I'll take the first flight tomorrow

742
00:37:56,579 --> 00:37:57,659
