743
00:37:59,219 --> 00:38:00,020
Family issues?

744
00:38:03,219 --> 00:38:03,779
No.

745
00:38:03,779 --> 00:38:05,619
It's actually Zhao Mei.

746
00:38:06,139 --> 00:38:07,299
She needs me right now.

747
00:38:07,299 --> 00:38:08,179
So I...

748
00:38:16,104 --> 00:38:18,591
♪Gotta go on to better things♪

749
00:38:18,774 --> 00:38:20,903
♪You know how far you've gone♪

750
00:38:21,090 --> 00:38:23,430
♪In the fire you rise again♪

751
00:38:23,498 --> 00:38:25,764
♪You made it through the worst♪

752
00:38:26,124 --> 00:38:28,202
♪The best is yet to come♪

